<view class="page-container">
  <view class="about-header">
    <view class="app-name">寻公问祖</view>
    <view class="version">版本 {{version}}</view>
    <view class="slogan">追溯根源，铭记先祖</view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">功能特点</view>
    <view class="feature-list">
      <view class="feature-item">
        <text class="feature-icon">🌳</text>
        <text class="feature-text">族谱树可视化 - 直观展示家族成员关系树状图</text>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-item">
        <text class="feature-icon">👥</text>
        <text class="feature-text">成员管理 - 增删改查家族成员信息</text>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-item">
        <text class="feature-icon">📖</text>
        <text class="feature-text">迁徙故事 - 记录和展示家族迁徙历史</text>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-item">
        <text class="feature-icon">🪦</text>
        <text class="feature-text">墓碑纪念 - 管理墓碑位置、记录扫墓祭扫</text>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-item">
        <text class="feature-icon">📷</text>
        <text class="feature-text">头像管理 - 支持成员头像上传、预览、删除</text>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-item">
        <text class="feature-icon">💾</text>
        <text class="feature-text">数据缓存 - 本地缓存加速加载，支持数据版本同步</text>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-item">
        <text class="feature-icon">☁️</text>
        <text class="feature-text">云端存储 - 图片等文件存储在云端</text>
      </view>
      <view class="feature-item">
        <text class="feature-icon">📍</text>
        <text class="feature-text">GPS定位 - 支持墓碑位置定位和导航</text>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">技术栈</view>
    <view class="tech-list">
      <view class="tech-item">微信小程序原生开发</view>
      <view class="tech-item">微信云开发（数据库、云存储、云函数）</view>
      <view class="tech-item">JavaScript</view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">开源地址</view>
    <view class="repo-box">
      <text class="repo-url">https://github.com/gaohouping-afk/mp_xztg</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">联系作者</view>
    <button open-type="contact" class="contact-button">
      <view class="contact-wrapper">
        <view class="contact-box">
          <view class="contact-icon">💬</view>
          <view class="contact-info">
            <text class="contact-text">联系作者</text>
            <text class="contact-hint">点击联系作者</text>
          </view>
          <text class="contact-arrow">›</text>
        </view>
      </view>
    </button>
  </view>

  <view class="section">
    <view class="section-title">关于开源</view>
    <view class="about-content">
      <text>本项目为开源项目，基于 GPL 协议开源。</text>
      <text>\n</text>
      <text>您可以免费使用、复制、修改和分发本项目代码。</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="footer">
    <text>© 2026 寻公问祖</text>
  </view>
</view>